Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.45,ammo - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur4}This is fate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:24.99,ammo - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)\blur4}Hello Mellow 甘い果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:32.19,ammo - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur4}この痛みも今年味を求めている
